ever a new location update is received by the map view. This method is also","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"called if the map view’s user tracking mode is set to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithHeading","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" and the heading changes, or if it is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"set to ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" and the course changes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This method is not called if the application is currently running in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"background. If you want to receive location updates while running in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"background, you must use the Core Location framework.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:didupdateuserlocation:"]}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:didUpdateUserLocation:","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L567"},"roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:didUpdateUserLocation:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"mapView:didUpdateUserLocation:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:didUpdateUserLocation:"}],"symbolKind":"method"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapVi